IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. ACTIVATE-POLICY.
AUTHOR. HEALTHINSURE CORE TEAM.

ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-EXPECTED   PIC 9(10).
01 WS-PAID       PIC 9(10).
01 WS-OUTPUT     PIC X(200).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY 1 UPON ARGUMENT-NUMBER.
    ACCEPT WS-EXPECTED FROM ARGUMENT-VALUE.
    DISPLAY 2 UPON ARGUMENT-NUMBER.
    ACCEPT WS-PAID FROM ARGUMENT-VALUE.

    IF WS-PAID >= WS-EXPECTED
        STRING '{"status": "VERIFIED", "message": "Payment confirmed. Policy activated."}'
            DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO WS-OUTPUT
    ELSE
        STRING '{"status": "REJECTED", "message": "Paid amount is less than the required premium."}'
            DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO WS-OUTPUT
    END-IF.

    DISPLAY FUNCTION TRIM(WS-OUTPUT).
    GOBACK.
